headline: Arista Networks (ANET) Down 18.8% Since Last Earnings Report: Can It Rebound?

headline: My Top 5 Stocks to Buy Right Now
summary: With the stock market in turmoil as economic uncertainty ramps up, long-term investors have an opportunity to pick up high-quality stocks at attractive prices.  My top five stocks include Intel (NASDAQ: INTC), AT&T (NYSE: T), International Business Machines (NYSE: IBM), Berkshire Hathaway (NYSE: BRK.B), and Paycom (NYSE: PAYC).
